            "title": "O papel do brincar na apropria\u00e7\u00e3o da linguagem escrita",
            "abstract": [
                "Na obra, a brincadeira se fortalece como objeto de estudos e como guia para movimentos essenciais nos processos vitais \u00e0 constitui\u00e7\u00e3o da intelig\u00eancia e da personalidade na inf\u00e2ncia, configurando bases fundamentais \u00e0 aprendizagem da linguagem escrita em sua vivacidade. Trata-se de uma composi\u00e7\u00e3o textual potencializadora de debates necess\u00e1rios em torno do papel social da escola dedicada \u00e0 crian\u00e7a pequena \u2013 particularmente aquela em idade pr\u00e9-escolar, dos lugares de seus agentes intelectuais (equipe, professoras e professores e outros profissionais atuantes no ambiente escolar) e da crian\u00e7a no ambiente educativo. No seio das discuss\u00f5es firmam-se avan\u00e7os cient\u00edficos e pol\u00edticos sobre o valor desse ambiente escolar como espa\u00e7o potencialmente organizado para fomentar condi\u00e7\u00f5es necess\u00e1rias e favor\u00e1veis \u00e0 constitui\u00e7\u00e3o humana \u2013 de adultos e crian\u00e7as \u2013 em sua inteireza e plenitude. O teor do livro convoca-nos, assim, a revisitar certezas e ideias do senso comum, considerando quest\u00f5es e tens\u00f5es sociais, econ\u00f4micas, pol\u00edticas, sanit\u00e1rias da atualidade e perspectivando o compromisso \u00e9tico, pol\u00edtico e social de atuarmos na dire\u00e7\u00e3o da forma\u00e7\u00e3o de intelig\u00eancias e personalidades harm\u00f4nicas desde o come\u00e7o da vida. Esse processo educativo tem car\u00e1ter revolucion\u00e1rio e emancipat\u00f3rio \u2013 ainda que tenhamos consci\u00eancia das for\u00e7as contr\u00e1rias e alienadoras fortalecidas por uma sociedade capitalista como a nossa \u2013 porque se refaz a cada dia para fortalecer condi\u00e7\u00f5es concretas e efetivas \u00e0 forma\u00e7\u00e3o plena de crian\u00e7as e dos profissionais que as educam",
                "In the work, play is strengthened as an object of study and as a guide for essential movements in vital processes for the constitution of intelligence and personality in childhood, setting up fundamental bases for learning written language in its vivacity. It is a textual composition that enhances necessary debates around the social role of the school dedicated to small children - particularly those of preschool age, from the places of their intellectual agents (staff, teachers and other professionals working in the school environment ) and the child in the educational environment. Within the discussions, scientific and political advances are established on the value of this school environment as a potentially organized space to foster necessary and favorable conditions for the human constitution \u2013 of adults and children \u2013 in its entirety and fullness. The content of the book thus invites us to revisit common sense certainties and ideas, considering current social, economic, political, and health issues and tensions and putting in perspective the ethical, political and social commitment of acting towards the formation of intelligences and harmonious personalities from the beginning of life. This educational process has a revolutionary and emancipatory character \u2013 even though we are aware of the opposing and alienating forces strengthened by a capitalist society like ours \u2013 because it is repeated every day to strengthen concrete and effective conditions for the full training of children and the professionals who educate them"
            ],
